    "northStar": "The Warp Lane / 跃迁车道",
    "overview": "cdp behaves like a high-speed wayfinding system for developer context. Commands are routes, projects are destinations, and every interaction ends in a visible arrival state. The system uses committed blue surfaces, rare signal yellow, and real terminal evidence without falling into dark SaaS or cyberpunk shorthand.",
